<h1>macd<h1>
Macd lagging indicator ne yana moving with market price  ' traders suna Gane reversal ko  strength/weak na kasuwa ta inda macd yayi declined/changing direction  na tafiya
MACD POSITIVE/NEGATIVE DIVERGENCE
POSITIVE 
Lokacin da kasuwa take downtrend Price zai tafi zuwa new low but idan ka duba macd sai aga shi Bai tafi kasa zuwa new low ba ' is considered bullish signal 
NEGATIVE
Lokacin da kasuwa take uptrend price zai tafi zuwa new high Amma macd zaiqi binsa zuwa new high ' is considered bearish signal
MACD BULLISH DIVERGENCE 
Lokacin da market take downtrend sai price yayi forming two falling lows but macd  yayi forming two rising highs' is considered bullish signal 
MACD BEARISH DIVERGENCE 
Lokacin uptrend  sai price yayi forming na two rising highs but MACD sai yayi forming na two falling lows ' is considered bearish signal
MACD CROSSOVER 
Idan aka duba macd za'aga layukane guda biyu suna tafiya ajikin juna akwai blue akwai yellow 
Blue ana kiransa da macd line 
Yellow ana kiransa da signal line  
Idan macd line yayi Cross above signal line is considered bullish signal 
Idan macd line yayi Cross below signal line is considered bearish signal
Mostly traders sunfi consider na Macd crossover lokacin da kasuwa take bullish sosai ko bearish' sosai
HISTOGRAM 
Idan anlura duk lokacin da aka kunna macd za'aga akwai wani shadow na candlestick suna biye dashi suna forming na green and red duk inda macd yayi zasu bishi idan yayi sama green zasuyi sama  idan yayi qasa red zasuyi qasa  traders suna amfani da inda wannan candlestick ya kasance Basu da tsayi sosai domin tabbatar da buy or sell signal 
Conclusion 
Yana da kyau ayi amfani da wasu indicators domin tabbatar da faruwar Macd kamar RSI ko ema ' Macd wata alamace ta sanin tafiyar kasuwa domin samun gwarin guiwa '' Macd yana da wasu alamomin Amma wannan sune alama mafi muhimmanci dukkan wani strategy yanada amfani kasanshi domin koba dashi kake aiki ba zaiyi maka amfani wata Rana ' ko banxa idan ka kalleshi kasan me yake nufi akwai YouTube channel da zamu saki a wannan satin insha Allah domin zamu koma topic cikin bidiyo 
Allah yabamu sa'a